德 (Ariana Grande</a> ) 的演出<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-bieber-breaks-hiatus-by-joining-ariana-grande-on-stage-at-coachella-2479358">中担任嘉宾</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-justin-bieber-join-daniel-caesar-for-performance-of-peaches-at-coachella-3205954">在 2022 年</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/daniel-caesar">丹尼尔·凯撒 (Daniel Caesar)</a>合作演唱了热门歌曲《Peaches》。</p><p>自从<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-bieber-reveals-facial-paralysis-from-ramsay-hunt-syndrome-3244867">2022 年透露自己因拉姆齐亨特综合症而患有面部麻痹以来，</a>比伯近年来一直保持低调。他最近拒绝在超级碗中场表演期间加入亚瑟<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/usher">小子</a>，尽管这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/usher-says-he-understands-why-justin-bieber-turned-down-super-bowl-offer-3588952">R&amp;B 明星表示他“理解”原因</a>，并补充道：“压力很大。” </p><figure id="attachment_3102875" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3102875" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3102875" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/tems-breakout-featured.jpg" alt="特姆斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/tems-breakout-featured.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/tems-breakout-featured-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/tems-breakout-featured-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/tems-breakout-featured-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/tems-breakout-featured-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/tems-breakout-featured-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3102875" class="wp-caption-text"> Tems（图片：媒体）</figcaption></figure><p>在演出期间的其他地方，Tems 表演了《Crazy Tings》、《Avoid Things》、《Replay》、《Me &amp; U》和《Free Mind》等热门歌曲。</p><p>今年科切拉音乐节的其他惊喜客串亮点包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/j-balvin">J Balvin</a>邀请<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/will-smith">威尔·史密斯</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/will-smith-joins-j-balvin-for-perfomance-of-men-in-black-theme-song-at-coachella-2024-3617782">演唱<em>《黑衣人》</em>主题曲</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/renee-rapp">Reneé Rapp</a>邀请<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kesha">Kesha</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kesha-joins-renee-rapp-for-a-cover-of-tik-tok-at-coachella-2024-3617660">翻唱后者的热门歌曲《Tik Tok》</a> ，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Olivia-Rodrigo">奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo)</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/no-doubt">No Doubt</a>一起表演乐队演出期间的“沐浴水”。</p><p>要了解 2024 年 Coachella 音乐节第一个周末的最新动态，请<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/coachella">在此处查看<em>NME</em>的报道</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tems-announces-debut-album-born-in-the-wild-3618320">Tems 宣布首张专辑《Born In The Wild》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
